"hash_answer" : "Ein Hash (oder eine TX-ID) ist eine eindeutige Transaktionsadresse, die in einer Blockchain aufgezeichnet ist und belegt, dass die Transaktion stattgefunden hat. Normalerweise besteht ein Hash aus einer Kombination von Ziffern und Kleinbuchstaben (Großbuchstaben bei Ripple). Wann immer Sie eine Zahlung in Kryptowährung tätigen, erhalten Sie einen Hash, der in Ihrer Brieftasche angezeigt wird.

Jeder Hash sollte sich in einer Blockchain befinden. Wenn Sie Probleme mit Ihrer Transaktion auf unserer Plattform haben, werden Sie möglicherweise von unserem Support-Team aufgefordert, den Hash für die Transaktion anzugeben, um Ihre Zahlung zu ermitteln und das Problem zu beheben."

"hash_answer" : "Un hash (o tx ID) es una dirección de transacción única registrada en el blockchain, que prueba que la transacción ha tenido lugar. Por lo general, un hash es una combinación de dígitos y letras minúsculas (mayúsculas en el caso de Ripple). Cada vez que realiza un pago en criptomoneda, recibe un hash que se muestra en su billetera.

Cada hash debe ubicarse en un blockchain. Si tiene algún problema con su transacción en nuestra plataforma, nuestro equipo de soporte puede solicitarle que proporcione el hash de la transacción para encontrar su pago y resolver el problema."

playstore_details.title: Changelly: Buy Bitcoin BTC & Fast Crypto Exchange
playstore_details.description:
Since 2015, crypto exchange Changelly offers a range of products and services to swap and buy bitcoin instantly as well as 160+ other crypto. We work with the most reliable crypto exchanges servicing more than 2 million customers. We provide users with the best rates, a simple interface, and 24/7 live support.  
Changelly mobile app is an intuitively simple, fast & safe way to swap cryptocurrency in minutes. Get the best mobile app to buy bitcoin instantly or exchange crypto in a Couple of Minutes!

⚡  NON-CUSTODIAL CRYPTO EXCHANGE
We’re a non-custodial instant cryptocurrency exchange platform working with Bitcoin and 160+ altcoins. No need to create an account – all crypto transactions occur on the blockchain and require no additional checks. If you want to save your exchange history or reach out to our support team, registration is simple - only your email is required.

Changelly swap platform acts as an intermediary between different cryptocurrency exchanges and customers, providing the best possible exchange rates on the market.

🔐  BUY CRYPTOCURRENCY WITH CREDIT CARD
Do you want to buy Bitcoin and altcoins with a debit card (Visa/Mastercard), bank account? We are glad to offer you such an opportunity. Changelly makes buying Ethereum, Dogecoin, USDT, and plenty of popular crypto coins and tokens incredibly easy. 

Currently, our fiat-to-crypto marketplace aggregates all offers from Simplex, MoonPay, Indacoin, Coinify, and Wyre to purchase cryptocurrencies with USD and EUR smoothly. All these providers allow you to buy Bitcoin instantly at the best rates, and then we’re transferring coins right to your personal wallet.

🔸  FIXED & TRANSPARENT FEES
We do not charge any hidden or unreasonable fees. Just the 0.25% commission for the crypto exchange plus a small fee to send the transaction on the blockchain - that's it.

🔍 EXCHANGE 160+ COINS & TOKENS
With our mobile app, you can exchange more than 160 cryptocurrencies at the best rates on the market  Bitcoin (BTC), Bitcoin Cash (BCH), Ethereum (ETH), Litecoin (LTC), XRP, BNB, Monero (XMR), Tron (TRX), EOS, Cardano (ADA), Dash, Dogecoin (DOGE), Zcash (ZEC) and many more altcoins.

✓ Stablecoins ➡️ Tether (USDT), TrueUSD (TUSD), DAI, USD Coin (USDC), EURS Coin, Gemini Dollar (GUSD).
✓ Exchange or Buy Tokens ➡️ Maker (MKR), Basic Attention Token (BAT), Huobi Token (HT), PAX, OmiseGO (OMG), BTT, etc.

🎓 ENORMOUS LIQUIDITY
We work with several major players in the cryptocurrency exchange market, always ready to provide our customers with the amount of cryptocurrency they need at the moment.

✅ ONE-ON-ONE 24/7 SUPPORT
Feel free to contact us if you have any questions or would like to exchange a large amount of bitcoins or altcoins.

🎁  AFFILIATE PROGRAM
We offer an affiliate program with a 50% revenue share mechanism. If you are a large cryptocurrency-related service, influencer or a fintech resource and would like to join, contact us at Affiliate program support: affiliate@changelly.com

👉  FRIENDLY TO CRYPTO BEGINNERS
Want to learn more about the cryptocurrency market? Sign up for our free cryptocurrency course at Crashcourse:  where we share knowledge from leading crypto experts. Protect yourself from scammers and earn profits when purchasing cryptocurrency!

Enjoy the full crypto exchange service functionality in your phone!

Available in 🇺🇸 🇬🇧 English, 🇪🇸 Español, 🇵🇹 Português, Россия (🇷🇺 Russia), 한국 (🇰🇷 Korea), 中国 (🇨🇳 China), 香港 (🇭🇰 Hong Kong)

❤️  Help us make Changelly crypto exchange better!
Download, read, and feel free to leave your feedback. If you have any questions, please follow and contact us:
✓ Support

Take advantage of the crypto market, buy bitcoin instantly using Changelly crypto exchange.
